{"aid": "igkozhufaz744r", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 2, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i6uayl3vEOz", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-09T13:07:12Z", "content": "<p>请问两位老师&#xff0c;课堂思考题的截止时间能否延长一些&#xff1f;周三从上午第二大节开始整整一天都有课&#xff0c;一直持续到晚上21:00。可能无法在当天完成作业</p>", "subject": "课堂思考题截止时间"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": [], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446634761495, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-03-09T13:21:01Z", "id": "i71wd8igijo1zb", "tag_endorse": [], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-09T13:21:01Z", "content": "<p>设定截止时间是手段&#xff0c;不是目的。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>你的情况应该也是大多数学生的情况&#xff0c;我觉得有两个可以改进的方法&#xff1a;</p>\n<p>1 老师提前布置课堂思考题&#xff0c;比如周一的课在上周六就布置&#xff0c;周三的课在周一就布置&#xff0c;这样想提前做的同学可以提前做。</p>\n<p>2 课堂思考题延迟到第二天晚上24点。特别鼓励&#xff08;具体鼓励措施没想好&#xff09;同学在课堂上现场完成思考题&#xff08;当然同学也需要提前做些准备&#xff09;。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>请向老师和同学给出进一步的改进方法。</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}], "type": "question", "unique_views": 114, "created": "2015-03-09T13:07:12Z", "id": "i71vvggn7md3yj", "no_answer": 0, "nr": 55, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "upvote_ids": [], "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "folders": ["lab1"], "bucket_order": 2, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6uayl3vEOz", "when": "2015-03-09T13:07:12Z", "data": "i71vvggq58n3yk", "anon": "no", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "when": "2015-03-09T13:21:01Z", "data": "i71wd8ijmw31zc", "to": "i71vvggn7md3yj", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "tags": ["lab1", "student"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "tag_good": []}}